Port Notes:

----- version 1.20.3-3 -----
Rebuilt for perl-5.10.

----- version 1.20.3-2 -----
Rebuilt with gcc-3.4 and the X11 ports of the SDL libraries.
Now that this is X11-based, SDL::OpenGL support is now included.

----- version 1.20.3-1 -----
Turns out that SDL_perl-1.x and 2.x are incompatible, and those apps 
that want SDL_perl want 1.x.  So until those apps upgrade, here's 1.x
instead.
This version was built against perl-5.8.6.

----- version 2.1.0-1 -----
Initial release for Cygwin.  SDL::OpenGL was not built, as from the code 
it seems to want X11 GL while SDL is Win32API-based, and it failed its 
test when built.  Maybe that's what's meant in the BUGS file.  PTC.


Cygwin port maintained by:
http://sourceware.org/cygwinports/
